{"tid":1931885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情肆虐下堅持正統　義大利人寧願餓死也不吃夏威夷披薩","createTime":"2020-03-18T11:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T12:43:58.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc8781e4c3c9dc225a0d802e261dddf86712703","tid":1931885,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www-mirrormedia-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200317120338-24ba55d86419c72c507069f87cce58c6-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-mirrormedia-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200317120338-24ba55d86419c72c507069f87cce58c6-mobile.jpg&h=4a479506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在義大利人心目中，僅有拿坡里的披薩才是正宗。（Pexels提供）<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，義大利成為歐洲疫情最慘重國家，各地民眾爭相到市場搶購民生物資，就怕影響持續擴大，不過近日就有義大利網友在推特分享1張照片，在大家瘋搶食物時，夏威夷口味的披薩成為唯一滯銷商品，即便餓死也要堅持的精神讓不少人笑了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-mirrormedia-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200317121152-a5469bb6047b7f1084f6e7d191a47f80-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-mirrormedia-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200317121152-a5469bb6047b7f1084f6e7d191a47f80-mobile.jpg&h=07c8f5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即便民生物資被掃光，夏威夷口味披薩還是滯銷。（翻攝自推特）<br />\n在義大利人心目中，對於披薩的拿捏非常嚴謹，只有拿坡里披薩才算正宗，因為在過去，披薩是窮人的食物，配料相當簡單。義大利人對於所謂美式披薩，像是有鳳梨的夏威夷口味不屑一顧，視為邪門歪道，還有義大利駐英國大使甚至批評夏威夷披薩說：這是「次等食品」（second-rate food）。<br />\n<br />\n疫情肆虐狀況下，只見超市冰櫃裡其他糧食已被搶購一空，唯獨擺在最角落的「夏威夷披薩」滯銷，義大利網友則表示「我們可能都會死，但必須有尊嚴地做到這點，披薩上面絕對不能有鳳梨！」<br />\n<br />\n其實，夏威夷口味披薩為帕諾普洛斯（Sam Panopoulos）發明，他出生於希臘，後來移居加拿大，1962年在安大略省查塔姆市開餐館，並以罐頭鳳梨和火腿做成「夏威夷風情」披薩，大受歡迎，最後帕諾普洛斯於2017年逝世，享壽83歲。<br />\n<br />\n不過，除了義大利人不愛以外，現任冰島總統約翰尼森（Gudni Johannesson）也曾開玩笑說，如果他有權力，將會禁止廚師在披薩上放鳳梨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20200317edi019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20200317edi019&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF7PkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=d96fa9fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20200317edi019</a>"},{"pid":"c79e38cc60594fbc9c4c97d1fbb0faf9640da609","tid":1931885,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"明明Pizza落菠蘿先好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5d7eb5da6c0d094d266f4c81e6a70661891f6a","tid":1931885,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34449ac5cd66b0950e854e984e89d410efef77a5","tid":1931885,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"呢種堅持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bab8e43d7c9183e1bb55498f53e334b283e81a","tid":1931885,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8f847f3ac4ff34b910c1dbe6d3cb68b4cab226","tid":1931885,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"買完掉左粒菠蘿咪得"},{"pid":"fd43e5f44193d5d8e0fa323c956422a1fb2ac6db","tid":1931885,"uid":6329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d8f847f3ac4ff34b910c1dbe6d3cb68b4cab226","tid":1931885,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"買完掉左粒菠蘿咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"已經俾菠蘿沾污咗<br />\n正如我掉d屎落去再拎走然後叫你食一樣"},{"pid":"71acc734cc783adb0ad5eb93d37a50d0905e4220","tid":1931885,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"明明Pizza落菠蘿先好食<br />\n<br />\n